    "name": "Inkshade",
    "steam_appid": 3141310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意：本游戏目前仅支持英语。正在考虑本地化，但无法保证会推出其他语言版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/c49d238af563bce711b47e2d331dc555.avif?t=1765467053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras_big/c49d238af563bce711b47e2d331dc555.avif?t=1765467053 width=800 height=52 /></span>棋桌后面的生物坚持请你参与他们的木质棋盘游戏。在这款游戏中，你是一位船长，想要寻找一片仅以“深渊”之名示人的神秘领域。为了到达这样一个地方，你需要征服一片大陆，获取一艘飞船，并驶入被诅咒的空域。或者更确切地说，组建一支船员队伍，让他们为你代劳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/b6d40323adebb7ab674dc7b8d6478e05.poster.avif?t=1765467053\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/b6d40323adebb7ab674dc7b8d6478e05.webm?t=1765467053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将需要尝试不止一次才能击败游戏领主并夺取胜利，每一轮游戏都会与上一轮有所不同。不过，凭借策略、战术还有不懈坚持，你注定会实现自己的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/ee751569432324d84f80a1d688587de4.poster.avif?t=1765467053\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/ee751569432324d84f80a1d688587de4.webm?t=1765467053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras/a56f2f2213d3953b6775f8a8d84cd9aa.avif?t=1765467053\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141310/extras_big/a56f2f2213d3953b6775f8a8d84cd9aa.avif?t=1765467053 width=800 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化并升级一系列独特的棋子，将其部署到一个回合制策略棋盘游戏之中。这些棋子就是你的船员，他们会忠实执行你的命令。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着破解谜题寻找新职业的棋子，探索棋桌之外的昏暗厅堂。烦请忽略地毯上的黑暗污渍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过招募倒下的敌人来在每轮游戏途中为你的收藏增加新的棋子。他们的加入是否心甘情愿并不重要，因为他们照样会为你浴血奋战。</p></li></ul>",
